{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 657203, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你先定义必要休息吧，", "timestamp": 1607056714, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 657207, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "资本论前几章既视感。。。", "timestamp": 1607056769, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 657214, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为不少人觉得他们是让人加班的人而非加班的人", "timestamp": 1607056883, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 657276, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你每天雷打不动摸的那会儿鱼，就是休息刚需", "timestamp": 1607057550, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 657343, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我摸鱼不是为了休息，就是为了纯粹的摸鱼", "timestamp": 1607057962, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 657365, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: ……请你讲讲为什么摸鱼不算休息，两者的区分和界限", "timestamp": 1607058183, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 657493, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "滚，别代表清华的同学", "timestamp": 1607059546, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 657561, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 摸鱼是休息刚需？你是对摸鱼有误解嘛还是对刚需不明确？我休息的时候去睡觉或者运动算哪门子摸鱼", "timestamp": 1607060221, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 657564, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "多少沾点", "timestamp": 1607060244, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 657621, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 敢问您这会儿在干啥呢，在工作还是运动还是睡觉？您过去三个月每天刷知乎/公众号/b站/其他摸鱼时间合计统计一下，是不是日均2-3小时（可能有波动，但不会太少）？如果把这个额度克扣到每天5分钟，坚持20年，你觉得你能做到吗？如果这都不算刚需，那什么算？", "timestamp": 1607060752, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 657703, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 刚需不是“我觉得人应该如何分配时间”，而是“人实际上在如何分配时间”。宁可熬夜睡眠不足还是要刷手机浪费时间的人普遍存在，恰恰说明了“醒着浪费时间”是和“补充睡眠”差不多重要性的刚需的存在", "timestamp": 1607061423, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 657746, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 否定人“醒着浪费时间”的正当性，不但是资本主义异化人的要求，更是我们国家的文化惯性；文化惯性使得过劳伤国的问题，在中国甚连被提出和被定义都无比困难", "timestamp": 1607061875, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 657976, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我这会儿跑实验室摸鱼呢，有点看不懂宁的逻辑，什么充电五分钟耗时20年，这个克扣是张口就来的？是宁出面克扣还是愿意被克扣？看不懂你的刚需论，莫非是人是铁饭是钢，一顿不吃饿的慌？", "timestamp": 1607063850, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 657997, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 麻烦好好修修逻辑吧，实在是让人比较费解", "timestamp": 1607063980, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 658026, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "问题是禁止加班是不现实的，不禁止加班那总有人愿意加班的，所以无解", "timestamp": 1607064224, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 658046, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 不是刚需那你这会别摸呗", "timestamp": 1607064416, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 658049, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 张口就人身攻击，一定过的很不幸吧", "timestamp": 1607064513, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 658051, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 觉得不用摸还每天搁实验室摸，宁一定过的很撕裂吧", "timestamp": 1607064557, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 658055, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 喷人谁不会啊", "timestamp": 1607064577, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 658088, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 哈哈哈哈 想必dz深得体会，还是祝愿dz过得幸福。那我这会儿在实验室，算刚需摸鱼嘛？只是偶尔摸个鱼而已，溜了犯不着跟你辩经", "timestamp": 1607064981, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 658518, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 135833, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 说人话的时候乱吠，非得学狗叫才摇尾巴，啧啧啧", "timestamp": 1607069299, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 135833, "reply": 21, "tag": null, "text": "#135748\n清华的学生真的不觉得人有必要休息吗…", "timestamp": 1607056650, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1607069296, "url": "", "vote": {}}}